OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mainly dry and
OL,6,Fbright day with just the odd shower
OL,7,Faround. The showers will develop more
OL,8,Fwidely in the afternoon near the west
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers will become more
OL,12,Fwidespread through the evening,
OL,13,Fperhaps merging to longer spells of
OL,14,Frain. A mainly cloudy night with
OL,15,Ffurther showers spreading east.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,18,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,19,FHowever, it should become drier and
OL,20,Fbrighter during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
